item.description: How to contribute to this documentation # Hugo # This documentation is built on Hugo. Hugo is a really fast static site generator built by Go. You will need prior Hugo and Markdown knowledge to proceed. Hugo Documentation # The Hugo Documentation is pretty useful for learning hugo. You don’t need to know all the details. Just basic hugo commands, file directory, and how to write new pages.
